    <name>ProtonPlus</name>
    <developer_name>Vysp3r</developer_name>
    <summary> A simple Wine and Proton-based compatiblity tools manager for GNOME </summary>
    <description>
        <p>ProtonPlus a simple Wine and Proton-based compatiblity tools manager for GNOME. It works with Steam, Lutris, Heroic Games Launcher and Bottles. It was made in Vala with GTK4 and Libadwaita using GNOME Builder.</p>
        <p>This project is still in its early phase, so please keep that in mind before using it.</p>
    </description>

